snippet.title: Brain Dead 13 - Full autoplay with (almost) all death sequences - Dos version -1995
snippet.description:
Brain Dead 13, Full game autoplay.
1995, PC (MS-DOS)

Directed and produced by Dave Quesnelle, developed and published by Readysoft.
Music by Brian Jack.

Only death sequence missing is the falling piano at the end, when you don't exit the castle.
EDIT: And the skeleton/shark ones by Fritz when idle for too long... Thanks to Karis AsaNi for noticing this!

PS: For cheat mode access, just hold the Ctrl key and type 'Readysoft' on the menu screen.
